{"word":"G2314 - θεομάχος - theomáchos - theh-om'-akh-os - To fight against God","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">θεομάχος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">theomáchos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">theh-om'-akh-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">To fight against God</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"தேவனோடு போர் செய்கிற - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"fighting against God, resisting God"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2316 - θεός - theós - theh'-os/2316\">G2316</a> and <a href=\"#/G3164 - μάχομαι - máchomai - makh'-om-ahee/3164\">G3164</a>; an <i>opponent of deity:</i> - to fight against God.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2313/2313\">G2313</a>, <a href=\"#/G2314/2314\">G2314</a>, <a href=\"#/G269/269\">G269</a>, <a href=\"#/G3163/3163\">G3163</a>, <a href=\"#/G3164/3164\">G3164</a>"}]}